descriptor.name: Portronics Toad One Bluetooth Mouse with 2.4 GHz & BT 5.3 Dual Wireless
descriptor.short_desc: Portronics Toad One Bluetooth Mouse with 2.4 GHz & BT 5.3 Dual Wireless, 6 Buttons, Rechargeable, RGB Lights, Connect 3 Devices, Ergonomic Design for Laptop, Smartphone, Tablet (Black)"
descriptor.long_desc:
[WIRELESS FREEDOM] - Enjoy up to a 10-meter wireless connection with the Toad One wireless mouse’s tiny plug-and-forget nano dongle. No software or driver installation is needed. The mouse automatically connects to your computer system. It is ready to go when you are.
[ADJUSTABLE DPI RESOLUTION] - With the button to adjust DPI resolution, now adjust your mouse sensitivity as per your requirement. This feature gives you more room to enhance your gaming skills and even work on editing with pixel-based simplicity.
[CARRY IT ANYWHERE, EVERYWHERE] - Toad One wireless optical mouse is the perfect accessory for those who travel for work, executives who give presentations, or anyone who wants greater control and freedom.
[ADDING COLOURS TO LIFE] - This wireless optical mouse comes with a lighting feature to make your working experience a colourful one. Moreover, Toad One gives you 7 coloured light functionality to adjust the lighting as per your desire.
[BATTERY THAT DOESN’T DIE EASILY] - This optical sensor mouse comes with a rechargeable battery through its Type-C charging port. Now work seamlessly for up to 9 days without any breaks or disruption

descriptor.name: Portronics Toad III Wireless Mouse with Bluetooth & 2.4 GHz Dual Connectivity, Rechargeable
descriptor.short_desc: Portronics Toad III Wireless Mouse with Bluetooth & 2.4 GHz Dual Connectivity, Rechargeable, 6 Buttons, Adjustable DPI, Silicon Grip & Ergonomic Design for PC, Laptop, Mac (Black)
descriptor.long_desc:
Wireless Freedom: Enjoy the convenience of using Portronics Toad III, a wireless mouse that can connect in two ways: via Bluetooth and a 2.4 GHz USB receiver. No tangled wires, no hassle!
Extended Working Range: With a remarkable range of up to 10 meters, you can control your device from a distance, giving you the freedom to work and play without being tied to your screen.
Multi-Device Pairing: The Toad III wireless mouse lets you pair with two devices simultaneously. One device with Bluetooth 5.3 and another device with the 2.4 GHz USB Receiver.
Universal Compatibility: This mouse works with iOS, MacOS, Windows, and Android devices. It's compatible with a wide range of gadgets like tablets, phones, monitors, and laptops.
Customized Precision: Adjust your mouse's sensitivity with ease, thanks to the adjustable DPI feature, which goes up to 1600, giving you the best of professional, academic, and casual experiences.

descriptor.name: Portronics Toad IV Bluetooth Mouse with 2.4 GHz Wireless (Dual Connectivity)
descriptor.short_desc: Portronics Toad IV Bluetooth Mouse with 2.4 GHz Wireless (Dual Connectivity), Rechargeable, Connect up to 3 Devices, RGB Lights, Adjustable Optical DPI, for Laptop, PC, Tablet, Smartphone (White)
descriptor.long_desc:
Wireless Connectivity: Using the latest wireless technology, the Portronics Toad IV wireless mouse can connect to your devices wirelessly using the 2.4 GHz USB receiver or Bluetooth. Enjoy a working range of up to 10 metres.
Triple Device Pairing: Pair the mouse with up to 3 devices at one time, one using the 2.4 GHz USB receiver, and the other two using Bluetooth. It is compatible with Laptop, PC, Mac, Tablets, and Smartphones.
Type-C Charging: This wireless mouse has a long battery life. You can charge it using the included Type-C Charging Cable. Connect the Type C end of the cable to the mouse’s charging port and the other end to any compatible power source.
Silent Clicks: Features silent clicks so that you can work quietly, and eliminate noise and distractions for yourself and others around you, especially while working at night. It is ideal for use at -home, office, library, & other places.
Colorful RGB Lights: The wireless optical mouse comes with Dynamic RGB Lights with 2 modes. You can easily switch between them and enjoy an enhanced working experience.

descriptor.name: Portronics Toad Ergo Vertical Advanced Wireless Ergonomic Mouse
descriptor.short_desc: Portronics Toad Ergo Vertical Advanced Wireless Ergonomic Mouse 2.4Ghz, 6D Button, Wrist Support, Adjustable DPI Upto 1200, Supports Hand Posture(Black)
descriptor.long_desc:
[HAPPY HANDS] : The wireless mouse has been designed to reduce the strain off your palms and hands. The vertical or handshake grip gives support to your palms and wrists to keep them comfortable for those long days at work.
[1200 DPI] : The ergonomic mouse has a DPI of 1200 which is ideal for casual gaming, academic and professional work. College assignments or work projects complete it without compromising on comfort.
[6D BUTTONS] : The button design is a mix of traditional and modern sensibilities, the 3 buttons Left, right and scroll wheels that is super sensitive and register all clicks and scroll. The DPI button to adjust cursor speed and 2 buttons on the left to go forward/backwards while working on an application or while browsing.
[EFFORTLESS COMPATIBILITY] : The ergonomic mouse is compatible with Windows and mac powered devices.
[POWER SAVING DESIGN] : The ergonomic mouse is powered by 2 AAA batteries and has a power-saving design. As soon as the mouse is not in use, it hibernates to save battery.

descriptor.name: Portronics Toad II Bluetooth Mouse, with Bluetooth 5.0 & 2.4 Ghz Dual Wireless Connectivity
descriptor.short_desc: Portronics Toad II Bluetooth Mouse, with Bluetooth 5.0 & 2.4 Ghz Dual Wireless Connectivity, Rechargeable Battery, Adjustable DPI up to 1600 Compatible with Laptop, MacBook, PC (Grey)
descriptor.long_desc:
Two-Way Street: The wireless mouse allows you to connect 2 ways - with 2.4 GHz (via USB Nano dongle) and Bluetooth 5.3. Toad II Wireless Mouse works for a range of up to 10 metres.
Multiple Device Pairing: This wireless mouse allows you to pair with one device via the 2.4 GHz USB Nano Dongle and up to two devices via Bluetooth.
Modify DPI: Toad II allows you to switch conveniently between Optical Tracking up to 1600 DPI. Toad II gives you the best of professional, academic and casual experiences.
Universal Compatibility: The mouse wireless is compatible with most operating systems like Windows, macOS and Linux. It is the perfect accessory to be used as a Bluetooth mouse for laptops.
Clever Design: The 5-button design with a left-right click, scroll wheel, DPI button and another button to switch between connections and devices (2.4 GHz and Bluetooth 5.3). The USB nano dongle fits in a slot designed inside the wireless mouse.

descriptor.name: HP K160 Wireless Keyboard
descriptor.short_desc: HP K160 Wireless Keyboard/Quick Comfy accurate/12 Fn Shortcut Keys/Plug and Play USB/ 3 Years Warranty, Black
descriptor.long_desc:
【WIRELESS KEYBOARD】Start typing in a snap with easy plug-and-play USB dongle connectivity.
【STYLISH DESIGN】Key into all-day comfort with a quiet keyboard that is ergonomically designed to keep your wrist in a natural comfortable position all day.
【SMART AND SILENT BUTTONS】Simplify your daily tasks with a keyboard featuring 12 Fn shortcut keys and a chiclet-style design for a quiet typing experience.
【VERSATILE COMPATIBILITY】Tap into smart connection and easy pairing with Windows XP and Windows Vista. Work comfortably on almost any device, wherever you are.
【RELIABLE WARRANTY】Type with peace of mind knowing that your keyboard is covered by a 3-year warranty with online support available 24x7. Consult the HP Customer Support Center for details.

descriptor.name: Logitech Pebble Keys 2 K380s, Multi-Device Bluetooth Wireless Keyboard
descriptor.short_desc: Logitech Pebble Keys 2 K380s, Multi-Device Bluetooth Wireless Keyboard with Customisable Shortcuts, Slim and Portable, Easy-Switch for Windows, macOS, iPadOS, Android, Chrome OS - Tonal Graphite
descriptor.long_desc:
Defy Boring: With a slim design, multiple colours and smarter tech, this Bluetooth keyboard from the Pebble 2 Collection lets you express your vibe and make your statement
Never Made Ordinary, Made to go places: the Pebble Keys 2 K380s keyboard is slim, compact, portable and made with recycled plastic (1)
Easily Hop Across 3 Devices: Use Bluetooth to connect up to 3 wireless devices across OSs (Windows, macOS, iPadOS, ChromeOS), and switch between them with one click of the Easy-Switch buttons
Save Time: Get instant access to search, screen capture, the emoji menu and more with Fn shortcut keys; personalise the 10 Fn keys with Logi Options+ app (2) so you can do things your way.
Go for Longer: This wireless keyboard gives you hours of use with a 3-year battery (3), auto-sleep power-saving mode, and 50% more battery life (4), for worry-free usage; batteries included
A Design Choice You’ll Feel Good About: Plastic parts in the Pebble Keys 2 K380s Slim Keyboard include minimum 49% certified post-consumer recycled plastic (1)
Responsibly-sourced packaging: The packaging of Pebble Keys 2 K380s (including product wrap) comes from FSC-certified forests and other controlled sources; certified carbon neutral

descriptor.name: Logitech MX Keys S Wireless Keyboard
descriptor.short_desc: Logitech MX Keys S Wireless Keyboard, Low Profile, Fluid Precise Quiet Typing, Programmable Keys, Backlighting, Bluetooth, USB C Rechargeable, for Windows PC, Linux, Chrome, Mac - Graphite
descriptor.long_desc:
Fluid Typing Experience: Laptop-like profile with spherically-dished keys shaped for your fingertips delivers a fast, fluid, precise and quieter typing experience
Automate Repetitive Tasks: Easily create and share time-saving Smart Actions shortcuts to perform multiple actions with a single keystroke with the Logi Options+ app (1)
USB C Rechargeable Keyboard: Stays powered for up to 10 days on a full charge or up to 5 months (backlighting turned off) (4); quick charge with the included USB-C charging cable
Team with Master 3S: Pair any MX wireless keyboard and mouse with Logi Options+ and seamlessly work, transfer text and files between up to 3 computers (Windows & macOS)
Recycled: Plastic parts in MX Keys S Wireless Keyboard include certified post-consumer recycled plastic — 26% for Graphite and 11% for Pale Grey (5)

descriptor.name: HP 450 Programmable Wireless, Full Size (Black)
descriptor.short_desc: HP 450 Programmable Wireless, Full Size; 3-Zone Layout Keyboard, 2.4 Ghz Wireless Connection, Compatible with Pcs with Available USB-A Port, Black
descriptor.long_desc:
Easy to Keep Clean and Sanitary: Will withstand 1,000 cleanings using disinfecting wipes.
Sleek, Stylish & Comfortable: Small adjustments make a big impact when it comes to typing accuracy. This sleek, stylish keyboard includes legs that can be adjusted by up to 6 degrees and contoured keycaps so you can strike the right key. Plus 2.0 mm travel delivers all-day comfort.
Customize to Optimize: Customize your keyboard with HP Accessory Center[1] to optimize how you work. Program 20+ keys with shortcuts so you can reduce keystrokes and work smarter in your most used apps.
Long Battery Life: Frequent battery changes are very frustrating. They can also drain your productivity and who needs that? Problem solved with a battery life that can last over 20 months
Sustainable Design Features: Responsibly designed, this keyboard helps reduce landfill waste by using post-consumer recycled materials that make up more than 60% of the plastics in the keyboard[2]. It’s all part of HP’s commitment to supporting cleaner air and waterways for a better world
